caption.paragraph:
FIGURE 5. Maximum-likelihood phylogram estimated from the COI dataset. Support values are shown on each branch: approximate Likelihood Ratio Test (aLRT) values and ML bootstrap (%) above, and Bayesian PP values below. Only values greater than 70% (aLRT), 70% (bootstrap) and 0.9 (PP) are shown, but all support values are shown if two support methods reach the cut-off value. Scale bar represents substitutions per site. GenBank accession numbers or BOLD accession number (for
Nicippe tumida
) are appended to taxon names.
